Playing around with a 6DOF IMU (MPU-6050), Arduino, Python and OpenGL


MPU-6050 gyro and accel setup and read.
Prints out to an LCD display X's when the gyro is at it's inital position in the x-y plane and arrows pointing the direction to bring it back to its inital position. 

MPU-6050 setup Forked from https://github.com/mattzzw/Arduino-mpu6050
